PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776326732
OL,3,CPatients treated in mobile endoscopy
OL,4,Cunits at hospital following fire
OL,6,FPatients are being treated in mobile
OL,7,Fendoscopy units at Southampton General
OL,8,Ffollowing a fire which destroyed the
OL,9,Fhospital's department ten weeks ago.
OL,11,FThe fire broke out shortly after
OL,12,F5.30am on Sunday 1 February in the
OL,13,Fendoscopy unit, caused by an
OL,14,Felectrical fault.
OL,16,FMore than 500 patients had to evacuate
OL,17,Fthe building as more than 110
OL,18,Ffirefighters got the fire under
OL,19,Fcontrol.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776326732
OL,3,CPatients treated in mobile endoscopy
OL,4,Cunits at hospital following fire
OL,6,FSince the fire, only emergency,
OL,7,Finpatient and therapeutic endoscopies
OL,8,Fhave been possible at the hospital
OL,9,Fafter two theatres and an area within
OL,10,Fthe Trust's Clinical Research Facility
OL,11,Fwere repurposed.
OL,13,FSome patients have also been seen by
OL,14,Fstaff, who were relocated, in
OL,15,Ftemporary sites including Royal South
OL,16,FHants, Spire, Nuffield and Lymington
OL,17,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776326732
OL,3,CPatients treated in mobile endoscopy
OL,4,Cunits at hospital following fire
OL,6,FHowever, two specialist mobile
OL,7,Fendoscopy units have now been
OL,8,Finstalled opposite the main entrance
OL,9,Fof Southampton General Hospital to
OL,10,Ftreat endoscopy patients.
OL,12,FThey have reception areas, consulting
OL,13,Fand procedure rooms as well as
OL,14,Frecovery areas.
OL,16,FUniversity Hospital Southampton NHS
OL,17,FFoundation Trust (UHS) have said it is
OL,18,Fa "significant milestone in the
OL,19,FTrust's recovery from the blaze".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776326732
OL,3,CPatients treated in mobile endoscopy
OL,4,Cunits at hospital following fire
OL,6,FThe temporary units will stay there
OL,7,Ffor at least two years as extensive
OL,8,Frepair work is carried out within the
OL,9,Fwest wing of the hospital.
OL,11,FAndy Hyett, chief operating officer at
OL,12,FUHS, said: "Bringing patients who
OL,13,Frequire these important diagnostic
OL,14,Ftests back to UHS is a real milestone
OL,15,Fin our recovery, which would not have
OL,16,Fbeen possible without the hard work
OL,17,Fand dedication of our staff.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776326732
OL,3,CPatients treated in mobile endoscopy
OL,4,Cunits at hospital following fire
OL,6,F"We appreciate the impact the
OL,7,Fdisruption caused by the fire has had
OL,8,Fon our patients and are grateful for
OL,9,Ftheir understanding and support during
OL,10,Fthe past ten weeks while we have
OL,11,Fdelivered as much of the service as
OL,12,Fpossible, in a different way.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776326732
OL,3,CPatients treated in mobile endoscopy
OL,4,Cunits at hospital following fire
OL,6,F"Our focus has always been on
OL,7,Freturning as much of this service, as
OL,8,Fquickly, safely and efficiently as we
OL,9,Fcan. This is the first step in
OL,10,Fbringing our patients and staff back
OL,11,Ftogether at UHS, while the Trust works
OL,12,Fon rebuilding the fire damaged area
OL,13,Fand creating a permanent home for
OL,14,Fendoscopy services in the future."
OL,16,FUHS said it continues to operate with
OL,17,F140 fewer beds because of the fire,
OL,18,Fwith part of west wing out of action
OL,19,Fand a number of services still
OL,20,Fdisrupted and displaced across the
OL,21,Fhospital site.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776326732
OL,3,CPatients treated in mobile endoscopy
OL,4,Cunits at hospital following fire
OL,6,FKat Black, specialist medicine matron
OL,7,Fat UHS, said: "This has been an
OL,8,Fexceptionally difficult period for
OL,9,Feveryone.
OL,11,F"We've faced uncertainty, ongoing
OL,12,Fpressure, and moments that have truly
OL,13,Ftested our resilience. What stands out
OL,14,Fmost is how we have worked together,
OL,15,Fas a team, never losing sight of what
OL,16,Fmatters most ` our patients.
OL,18,F"Even at our most challenging times,
OL,19,Fwe have seen unwavering
OL,20,Fprofessionalism, kindness, and
OL,21,Fcompassion.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776326732
OL,3,CPatients treated in mobile endoscopy
OL,4,Cunits at hospital following fire
OL,6,F"Colleagues across the organisation
OL,7,Fhave gone above and beyond and we want
OL,8,Fto thank everyone who has supported
OL,9,Fus."
OL,11,FWork is underway on land at Adanac
OL,12,FPark to open a further three mobile
OL,13,Fendoscopy units in June.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
